did.unittitle: Callender, Clifton. Point and Line to Plane

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Pieces included: 1 score, 1 CD. Notes: Received the CD in a separate original box from the score. CD was found in Original Box 5. CD was alone in an envelope with the titles: "Metamorphoses, Point and Line to Plane, Tre Balli, Luminous Signals, and Reflections on the Nature of Light" written on the outside of the envelope. The CD contains these pieces plus several more. .
